<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>Ab</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Bawi Jesuh nih hla dawh a ka pek, Van in a rungmi a si, Khi nak dawh
 deuh hla aw a um bal lo, Dawtnak hla aw thlum a si.

[C1]
   Ka lung chungah aw thlum a rung thang, Van aw thawng he aa remmi hla
   dawh cu a thang, Ka lung chungah aw thlum a rung thang, Dawtnak hla aw
   thlum a rung thang.

[V2]
 Kal-va-ry a thimi Khrih ka dawt, Ka sual a tawl dih caah, Ka lung
 chungah hla aw a khumh tak cang, Ka lung chung a um ka hngalh.

[C2]
   Ka lung chungah aw thlum a rung thang, Van aw thawng he aa remmi hla
   dawh cu a thang, Ka lung chungah aw thlum a rung thang, Dawtnak hla aw
   thlum a rung thang.

[V3]
 Sunparnak hla dong lo a si lai, Vancungmi he kan sak lai, Ngaih nuammi
 thangthatnak aw asi lai, Van darkhing an tum tikah.

[C3]
   Ka lung chungah aw thlum a rung thang, Van aw thawng he aa remmi hla
   dawh cu a thang, Ka lung chungah aw thlum a rung thang, Dawtnak hla aw
   thlum a rung thang.</lyrics>
<title>KA LUNG CHUNGAH AW THLUM A RUNG THANG CH393</title>
<hymn_number>393</hymn_number>
</song>